{"view":"article","slug":"pyraminx-keyhole","category":"Pyraminx","subcategory":null,"topDir":"Pyraminx","title":{"en":"Pyraminx Keyhole Method 金字塔空穴法"},"content":{"en":"<p><strong>Pyraminx Keyhole Method 金字塔空穴法</strong></p><p>S = R' L R L', H = L R' L' R. </p><p><strong><u>Two Edges on a Corner角上的两棱</u></strong></p><p>The edge to be solved in the image below is red-blue. Define keyhole as the unsolved edge on this corner. </p><p>图中要还原的棱为红蓝棱. 称该角上的未还原棱为空穴. </p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>R</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"Dw R'\"><strong>Dw R'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><strong>R'</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"Dw' R\"><strong>Dw' R</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' Dw R'\"><strong>R' Dw R'</strong></span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' L R\"><strong>R' L R</strong></span></p><p>L R</p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' U R\"><strong>R' U R</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' U' R\"><strong>R' U' R</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L R' L'\"><strong>L R' L'</strong></span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' L'\">R' L'</span></p></td><td><p><strong>Solved</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong><u>Bottom Centers底心</u></strong></p><p>Intuitively move 3 yellow centers to bottom face using keyhole (grey). </p><p>利用空穴（灰色）凭直觉让三个黄心到底面. </p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>R'</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' Dw R\"><strong>R' Dw R</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' Dw R'\"><strong>R' Dw R'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' Dw R' Dw R\"><strong>R' Dw R' Dw R</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' Dw R' Dw R'\"><strong>R' Dw R' Dw R' </strong></span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image36.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image38.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image40.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>R</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R Dw R'\"><strong>R Dw R'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L Dw' L\"><strong>L Dw' L</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L Dw' L Dw' L'\"><strong>L Dw' L Dw' L' </strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L Dw' L Dw' L\"><strong>L Dw' L Dw' L</strong></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong><u>Keyhole空穴</u></strong></p><p>Non-yellow. 非黄色. </p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image42.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image44.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image46.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image48.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L' R' L R\"><strong>L' R' L R</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R L R' L'\"><strong>R L R' L'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><strong>H (L' U L)</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U S (R U' R')\">U S (R U' R')</span></p></td><td><p><strong>Solved</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong><u>ELL (Edges of Last Layer)</u></strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image50.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image52.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image54.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image56.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image58.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>S</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"z L' U L U'\">z L' U L U'</span></p></td><td><p><strong>H</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"z' R U' R' U\">z' R U' R' U</span></p></td><td><p><strong>H (U' R U R')</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"S (U L' U' L)\">S (U L' U' L)</span></p><p>z H (L' U L U')</p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"z' S (R U' R' U)\">z' S (R U' R' U)</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"S (L' U L U')\"><strong>S (L' U L U')</strong></span></p></td><td><p><strong>H (R U' R' U)</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>"},"algs":["Dw R'","Dw' R","R' Dw R'","R' L R","R' U R","R' U' R","L R' L'","R' L'","R' Dw R","R' Dw R' Dw R","R' Dw R' Dw R'","R Dw R'","L Dw' L","L Dw' L Dw' L'","L Dw' L Dw' L","L' R' L R","R L R' L'","U S (R U' R')","z L' U L U'","z' R U' R' U","S (U L' U' L)","z' S (R U' R' U)","S (L' U L U')"],"thumb":"/stats/tutorial/media/pyraminx-keyhole/en/image2.svg","warningCount":1,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":true}
